%% CTUAV UAV Dock Client state machine (short form)

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE

    IDLE --> REQUESTING_DOCK: User kích request_dock
    REQUESTING_DOCK --> REQUESTING_DOCK: Service chưa có / reject / timeout retry
    REQUESTING_DOCK --> APPROACHING_DOCK: Response accepted hoặc DockState RESERVED
    APPROACHING_DOCK --> CONTACTED: DockContact true hoặc DockState CONTACTED
    CONTACTED --> IDLE: Contact false và ReleaseDock accepted

    APPROACHING_DOCK --> IDLE: DockState IDLE
    REQUESTING_DOCK --> IDLE: User kích release_dock

